I"<h1 id="account">Account</h1>

<h2 id="step-1-install-polkadot-chrome-extension">Step 1: Install Polkadot Chrome Extension</h2>

<p><strong>Use Chrome</strong></p>

<ul>
  <li>Go to: <a href="https://polkadot.js.org/extension/ ">https://polkadot.js.org/extension/ <a></a></a></li>
  <li>Click Download for Chrome</li>
</ul>

<p><img src="/assets/img/account/step1.png" /></p>

<h2 id="step-2-create-an-account">Step 2: Create an account</h2>

<p><strong>Using your Polkadot chrome wallet extension</strong></p>

<ul>
  <li>Click the plus sign in the top left.</li>
  <li>Choose Create new account.</li>
</ul>

<p><img src="/assets/img/account/step2a.png" /></p>

<ul>
  <li>Make sure you save your mnemonic seed phrase in a separate file.</li>
  <li>Once done saving, press the Next step.</li>
</ul>

<p><img src="/assets/img/account/step2b.png" /></p>

<ul>
  <li>Provide the name of your account.</li>
  <li>Provide a password and confirm it.</li>
  <li>Press Add the account.</li>
</ul>

<p><img src="/assets/img/account/step2c.png" /></p>

<ul>
  <li>Your account has been successfully created.</li>
</ul>

<p><img src="/assets/img/account/step2d.png" /></p>

<h2 id="step-3-open-humidefi-site">Step 3: Open Humidefi site</h2>

<ul>
  <li>Go to: <a href="https://www.humidefi.com/  ">https://www.humidefi.com/ <a></a></a></li>
  <li>Click <strong>Open App</strong></li>
</ul>

<p><img src="/assets/img/account/step3.png" /></p>

<h2 id="step-4-login">Step 4: Login</h2>

<p>Login using your Polkadot wallet account.  Donâ€™t forget to allow the site to be trusted by the wallet.</p>

<ul>
  <li>Click the Polkadot(.js) button.</li>
</ul>

<p><img src="/assets/img/account/step4a.png" /></p>

<ul>
  <li>Choose from the list of account you want to login.</li>
</ul>

<p><img src="/assets/img/account/step4b.png" /></p>

<ul>
  <li>Provide the password.</li>
</ul>

<p><img src="/assets/img/account/step4c.png" /></p>

<h2 id="step-5-portfolio">Step 5: Portfolio</h2>

<p>Welcome to Humidefi.</p>

<p><img src="/assets/img/account/step5.png" /></p>

